ZH: 这个礼物是我帮朋友代买的。
EN: This gift was purchased by me on behalf of a friend.

ZH: 我代替你去开会。
EN: I will attend the meeting in your place.

ZH: 他代表了整个团队的观点。
EN: He represented the views of the entire team.

ZH: 我们需要一位代课老师。
EN: We need a substitute teacher.

ZH: 她一直代表公司与客户交涉。
EN: She has been representing the company in negotiations with clients.

ZH: 律师是被告人的代理人。
EN: The lawyer is the defendant's legal representative.

ZH: 代沟是跨代交流中的一大问题。
EN: Generation gap is a major issue in intergenerational communication.

ZH: 我奉行代沟的理念。
EN: I believe in bridging the generation gap.

ZH: 代沟是由于文化差异所导致的。
EN: Generation gap is caused by cultural differences.

ZH: 我希望能够代表我们的议案。
EN: I hope to advocate for our proposal.

ZH: 她代言了一家化妆品公司。
EN: She endorsed a cosmetics company.

ZH: 他代表了所有的家人发言。
EN: He spoke on behalf of all the family members.

ZH: 这部电影代表了当代女性的力量。
EN: This movie represents the strength of contemporary women.

