EN: Representatives must be accountable for what they say.

ZH: 我们的代表在大会上发言。
EN: Our delegate will speak at the conference.

ZH: 你是我们团队的代表之一。
EN: You are one of the representatives of our team.

ZH: 代表们都达成了一致意见。
EN: The delegates reached a consensus.

ZH: 代理人必须严格尊重当事人的意愿。
